#CameLuxe is a frontier for mindful fashion and is founded through a process in which discarded camel hair fabrications are upcycled from #MaxMara's legendary outerwear to create a warm insulation for future coats. Explore CameLuxe in #MaxMaraTheCube's padded water-repellent coats now online at maxmara.com and in store.

In September 2019, Max Mara received recognition for sustainability from the Camera Nazionale della Moda Italiana for #CameLuxe at the Green Carpet Fashion Awards. Discover CameLuxe in #MaxMaraTheCube's latest water-repellent padded coats now at maxmara.com and in store.
